Package: gts
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Gridded Environmental Time-Series Analysis
Version: 0.2.9021
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Oliveros-Ramos",
           email = "ricardo.oliveros@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8069-2101"))
Description: Lightweight tools for handling gridded environmental data in
    ecological workflows, with particular emphasis on time-varying
    environmental drivers and time-invariant spatial covariates. The package
    provides classes and methods for importing, manipulating, summarising and
    exporting gridded data, especially from netCDF files, while preserving
    spatial and temporal metadata. Core workflows include subsetting,
    interpolation, regridding, climatology and time-series analysis, vertical
    integration, and merging gridded variables with observation records.
